### Our Strategic Approach

**Differentiation:** Every competitor treats "aesthetic nail ideas" as a trend catalogue — we treat it as an identity guide. The reader arrives not knowing their vibe; we leave them knowing exactly which aesthetic is theirs, and almond nails emerge as the shape that serves every one of them. This is the only pillar on the SERP that works as a true aesthetic-to-shape journey.

**Structure Plan:** Organise by named vibe/aesthetic (not by colour or finish), with each section functioning as both a standalone read and a gateway into a dedicated spoke post. Open with a clear "what is an aesthetic nail" framework, then move through the full vibe spectrum from understated to maximalist. Each section tells the reader what the aesthetic *feels like* before showing what it looks like.

**Tone Direction:** Nail-obsessed editor meets aesthetic translator — confident, visual, never condescending. Speaks to the woman who knows she has a vibe but needs the language for it.

